### 3. Seller Dashboard Page Structure

**Location:** `frontend/src/app/seller/stores/[storeId]/page.tsx`

**Layout:**
- **Header**: "Store" title with back link to `/seller` and Settings button
- **Tab Navigation**: Two tabs ‚Äî "Pickups" (default) and "Manage"

**Pickups Tab Contents:**
