- GlobalPickupEntry (QR code scanning for pickups)
- Payout summary line item ("Today: $X from N pickups")
- OrderList (orders for selected window with status management)

**Manage Tab Contents:**
- SubscriptionPlanList (plan cards with pause/resume/generate cycle actions)
