- Shows "X.X from N review(s)" text
- Default styling: `inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--lr-muted)]`
- Custom className overrides default styling

**Additional Components in Same File:**
- `StarRating({ rating })` ‚Äî renders 1-5 star icons (filled/gray based on rating)
- `ReviewCard({ review })` ‚Äî renders individual PublicReview with rating, timestamp, and body text

### 5. Existing Seller API Functions (signatures only)

