- BoxPreview type already exists with `id`, `plan_id`, `cycle_date`, `body`, `photo_url`, `created_at`, `updated_at`
- API functions `listBoxPreviews` and `createBoxPreview` already exist
- ReviewSummary component is reusable for star display
- Seller dashboard "Manage" tab is the logical placement for box preview posting UI
